data.description: Great Folsom Bluffs Condo with amazing Canyon views!! Absolutely stunning home! featuring 4 beds + flex room, 3 full baths. As you enter 1st floor you will be greeted with abundance of natural light through out the inviting floor plan w/great room concept. Adjacent dinning area overlooking living & family rooms w/views of Canyon and Greenbelt. Enjoy the open air atrium for all your beautiful flowers/plants. There is also a bedroom and full bath located on first floor with front patio access for your morning coffee. Upstairs you will find additional bedrooms including Spacious Main bedroom w/ floor to ceiling windows giving amazing views of the Canyon, en suite bath & walk in closet plus your own private balcony. New HVAC unit in 2022. Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity to own this beautiful home located on greenbelt steps away from Folsom lake hiking & biking trails in desirable Folsom Bluffs.
